quran[60]{c,v,t}:
  51,1,"Nditsuba khumuyeka (imbumbuyeka) kusalaasinjia,"
  51,2,"Nende kuchinganga emikuku,"
  51,3,"Nende kuwutsanga khubwangu,"
  51,4,"Okukabaanga shinga kulomesibwe."
  51,5,"Toto kamulakungwa nikahabwene."
  51,6,"Ne toto Inyanga yomurungo ilibaho."
  51,7,"Nditsuba khulikulu lili nende tsinjila,"
  51,8,"Toto enywe muli mumakhuwa kawukhaane."
  51,9,"Ukalukhanibwa okhurula khubwatoto akalukhanibwa."
  51,10,"Abachishi balisishibwa."
  51,11,"Balia bakoyanila mubusilu."
  51,12,"Barebanga mbu: “Ni lina inyanga yomurungo?”"
  51,13,"Inyanga eyo balinyoola eshinyasio shiomulilo."
  51,14,"“Pile eshinyasio shienyu shino eshamwayungubalilanga.”"
  51,15,"Toto balia baria Nyasaye baliba mumikunda chomwikulu nende tsisebele."
  51,16,"Ne balibukula ka Nyasaye abahele, toto imbeli awo abo bali abakholi bamalayi."
  51,17,"Bakonanga hatiti eshilo."
  51,18,"Ne eshilo nishitsia okhushia, balamanga nibasaba eshileshelo."
  51,19,"Ne mumiandu chiabu omukabo kwa abasabi nende balasabanga kwalimwo."
  51,20,"Ne khushialo biliwo ebimanyisio khubasuubila toto."
  51,21,"Nende khumibili chienyu. Koo, shimulolangakhwo tawe?"
  51,22,"Ne mwikulu kuliyo omukabo kwenyu, nende kamulakungwa."
  51,23,"Kho, nditsuba khu Nyasaye Omulesi welikulu nende eshialo, mbu toto kano nikahabwene shinga enywe muboolanga."
  51,24,"Koo, lwakhuulilakhwo olukano lwa abacheni ba Ibrahim boluyali?"
  51,25,"Olwa benjila ewuwe nibaboola mbu: “Mulembe.” Naye nabakalusia mbu: “Mulembe muno Abandu bengorerwe.”"
  51,26,"Natsia khubandu be, niyetsa nende eshimosi shianera."
  51,27,"Nabasitilia hambi eshiakhulia, nabareba mbu: “Shimulitsanga tawe?”"
  51,28,"Naba noburi khubo, nibamuboolela mbu: “Olaria tawe.” Ne nibamubolera komwikhoyo koomusiani wobumanyi po."
  51,29,"Nilwa omukhasi wuwe yabachoma, nawuka, niyepama obweni, naboola mbu: “Esie omushiele mana omukumba ndakhebula endie?”"
  51,30,"Nibaboola mbu: “Endio nilwa kali, nilwa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi aboolele. Toto niye Owamachesi muno, Omumanyi po.”"
  51,31,"Naboola mbu: “Murumilwe shina enywe Abarumwa?”"
  51,32,"Nibabola mbu: “Toto efwe khurumilwe khubandu abetsimbi."
  51,33,"Khubalasile amachina keliloba."
  51,34,"Karebwakhwo eshimanyisio okhurula ewa Nyasaye wuwo Omulesi khulwa balia babura eshichelo.”"
  51,35,"Kho khwarusiamwo Abasuubili balimwo."
  51,36,"Ne shikhwanyoolamwo halali inzu ndala yonyene yabasalamu."
  51,37,"Ne nikhulekhamwo eshimanyisio khubalia baritsanga eshinyasio eshilulu."
  51,38,"Ne khulukano lwa Musa, olwa khwamuruma khu Firauni nende ebifune bia habulafu."
  51,39,"Nakhola obufuru khumaani keke naboola mbu: “Oli omulosi nohomba omulalu.”"
  51,40,"Ne nikhumutila nende omukanda kukwe kwabalwani, nikhubasukuna munyanza naye nali ufunaanibwa."
  51,41,"Ne (okhusishibwa khwa) Abandu ba A’ad, olwa khwabarumila omuyeka omukumba."
  51,42,"Shikwalekha shiosishiosi shiakwaburakhwo tawe, halali nikushikhola shinga eshindu shionoonibwe obubii muno."
  51,43,"Ne Abandu ba Thamudi, olwa baboolelwa mbu: “Mwikhoye khubise bititi.”"
  51,44,"Ne nibakhaya okhulonda amalako ka Nyasaye wabu Omulesi, mana likulu nilibakhupa nabo nibalolanga."
  51,45,"Mana shibanyala okhwema tawe, ne shibanyala okhwihabina tawe."
  51,46,"Ne Abandu ba Nuhu imbeli eyo. Toto bali Abandu baruuma eshichelo."
  51,47,"Ne likulu khwaliumbakha khumaani, ne toto efwe khuli nobunyali obushila ako."
  51,48,"Ne liloba khwaliala, ne khuli abaali abalayi balibarie efwe!"
  51,49,"Ne mubuli eshindu khwaloonga eshisaatsa neshikhasi kho munyoole okhwitsulila."
  51,50,"Kho ilushile ewa Nyasaye. Toto esie endi omwikanyilisi wenyu owa habulafu okhurulana ninaye."
  51,51,"Ne mulakholela Nyasaye nyasaye wundi tawe. Toto esie endi omwikanyilisi wahabulafu okhurulana ninaye."
  51,52,"Ne endio, shiyabetsela Omurumwa yesiyesi balia bali imbeli wabu tawe halali baboola mbu: “Oyo ni Omulosi nohomba Omulalu.”"
  51,53,"Ne koo, baboolanila kano? Halali bo ni Abandu baruma muno eshichelo."
  51,54,"Mana lekhana ninabo, nawe sholafunaanibwa tawe."
  51,55,"Ne itsulisia. Toto ametsulisio kakhoonyanga Abasuubili."
  51,56,"Ne shindaloonga Amajini nende Abandu tawe halali khulwa baalame esie."
  51,57,"Shebenyakhwo omukabo tawe, ne shindenya bandisie tawe."
  51,58,"Toto Nyasaye niye Omukabi muno, Owamani amanji muno."
  51,59,"Ne toto balia abamabii, bali nende tsimbi tsiabu shinga tsimbi tsia abaashiabwe, kho balaayungubasia tawe."
  51,60,"Kho eshinyasio eshikhongo shili khubalia bakhaya okhurulana nende inyanga yabu yabalakwa."
